    id: 23, slug: "moringa-affiliate-business-blueprint", title: "Building a Moringa Powder Affiliate Business: Beginner's Blueprint", category: "Affiliate Marketing", date: "2026-03-24", readTime: "11 min", author: "Sachin Shinde", excerpt: "A complete 90-day action plan to build a moringa affiliate business from zero — no experience required.", thumbnail: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1589829085413-56de8ae18c73?w=600&q=80", seoTitle: "Moringa Affiliate Business Blueprint: 90-Day Action Plan", seoDesc: "90-day beginner-friendly blueprint to build a moringa powder affiliate business. Week-by-week action plan with tools and resources.", keywords: ["moringa affiliate business", "affiliate marketing beginners", "90 day affiliate plan"], content: `## 90-Day Moringa Affiliate Business Blueprint\n\n### Week 1-2: Foundation\n- Register on Amazon Associates, iHerb Affiliate, Avani Agro Foods Program\n- Create Instagram + YouTube channel\n- Write your first 3 blog posts (use our template guide)\n- Install Google Analytics and Search Console\n\n### Week 3-4: Content Creation\n- Record first YouTube video: "I tried Moringa Powder for 7 days"\n- Post daily Instagram stories about moringa benefits\n- Write 3 comparison articles for your blog\n- Create WhatsApp Business profile\n\n### Month 2: Traffic Building\n- Publish 2 blog posts per week (SEO)\n- YouTube: 2 videos per week\n- Instagram: 1 Reel per day\n- Guest post on 2-3 health blogs\n\n### Month 3: Monetization\n- Build email list (target 500 subscribers)\n- Send weekly newsletter with affiliate links\n- Apply for direct partnership with Avani Agro Foods\n- Analyze top-performing content and double down\n\n## Tools You Need (Free/Low Cost)\n| Tool | Purpose | Cost |\n|------|---------|------|\n| Google Blogger / WordPress | Blog | Free |\n| Canva | Graphics | Free |\n| Mailchimp | Email | Free (500 sub) |\n| Google Analytics | Traffic | Free |\n| TinyURL / Bitly | Link shortening | Free |\n| WhatsApp Business | Communication | Free |\n\n## 90-Day Income Projection\n- Month 1: ₹500-2,000 (small Amazon commissions)\n- Month 2: ₹2,000-8,000 (growing traffic)\n- Month 3: ₹8,000-25,000 (email list + multiple channels)\n- Month 6: ₹25,000-75,000 (scaled content machine)`
