    id: 24, slug: "social-media-health-affiliates", title: "Social Media Marketing Tips for Health Product Affiliates", category: "Affiliate Marketing", date: "2026-03-28", readTime: "8 min", author: "Sachin Shinde", excerpt: "Platform-specific social media strategies for health product affiliates — Instagram, YouTube, Pinterest, and WhatsApp.", thumbnail: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611926653458-09294b3142bf?w=600&q=80", seoTitle: "Social Media Tips for Health Product Affiliates (2026)", seoDesc: "Platform-by-platform social media marketing guide for health supplement and moringa affiliate marketers.", keywords: ["social media health affiliate", "instagram moringa marketing", "health product marketing tips"], content: `## Platform-Specific Strategies\n\n### Instagram\n- **Format**: Reels > Stories > Grid Posts\n- **Best content**: Before/After, recipes, unboxing, reactions\n- **Hashtags**: #moringapowder #healthandwellness #superfood #madeinindia\n- **Posting**: 1 Reel/day for maximum reach\n- **Bio**: Include affiliate link + clear CTA\n\n### YouTube\n- **Videos that convert**: Reviews > Challenges > Recipes\n- **Titles**: "I tracked my health for 30 days on Moringa"\n- **Cards & End Screens**: Link to affiliate product\n- **SEO**: Target "moringa powder review" keywords\n\n### Pinterest\n- **Evergreen traffic**: Pins rank for years\n- **Best content**: Infographics, recipes, benefit charts\n- **Group boards**: Join health and wellness boards\n- **Linked pins**: All pins link to affiliate reviews\n\n### WhatsApp\n- **Groups**: Share valuable tips, not just links\n- **Status**: Daily moringa facts + product link\n- **Broadcast**: Weekly "Wellness Wednesday" health tips\n- **Conversion**: Personal trust = high conversion\n\n## Content Calendar Template\n| Day | Content | Platform |\n|-----|---------|----------|\n| Monday | Moringa Benefit Fact | Instagram Reel |\n| Tuesday | Recipe | YouTube Short |\n| Wednesday | Review/Comparison | Blog |\n| Thursday | Testimonial | WhatsApp Status |\n| Friday | Product Deal | Email Newsletter |\n| Saturday | Q&A | Instagram Story |\n| Sunday | Rest or Repurpose | All |`
